{
  "stem": "11174.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I haven't come across anybody to sort of write about this in a serious way in more details because these chapter of the poor people running from town to town is a very, very interesting.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In every town it was different.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very colorful even, but I haven't heard or seen anybody that give it the-- the-- the deserved chapters, the deserved way of writing it out.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's name was Yehuda Sindel Lipschitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How was it for me?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Growing up-- you've got a good question and it's a little bit touchy and therefore I won't [LAUGHS] touch on it too much, I wouldn't, because he was very, very strict.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, when I was fairly young-- fairly young, I mean really young.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was-- it was not bad because he came home, especially wintertime from shul it was about 4:30.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was already after market, about quarter to 5:00.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came home, sat down to learn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "At night he got up and took the tallis and tefillin, went to shul in the morning.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That whole winter night was sitting and learning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the next day, the next morning, he came back from shul.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He ate some breakfast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then sometime and say he laid down for awhile.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then there was sometimes after he got up, there were always some rabbinical things to take care of, so he didn't have much time to me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I got bigger and the rabbinical [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] responsibilities and [? everything ?] was-- came larger, he didn't have that much time to sit the whole night and learn.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then my mother got a little ill, so it was different.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He had somehow, he was more busy with the rabbinate and therefore there was sometimes a little time.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
